        <h1 data-ref="privacy">
            Privacy<br><small><dfn>63a39b88-2603-4bce-ac5b-8247bf262986</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>63a39b88-2603-4bce-ac5b-8247bf262986</var> is an object that defines the privacy properties of an app.</p>

        <p>This object generally contains key-object pairs, where each object is itself a key-object pair. The outer keys represent "classificatons" of data that may be collected; the inner keys represent "types" of sharing that may occur; and the inner values represent if and how sharing is allowed.</p>

        <h3>Classifications</h3>

        <ul>
            <li><var>session</var></li>
            <li><var>context</var></li>
            <li><var>name</var></li>
            <li><var>contact</var></li>
            <li><var>preferences</var></li>
            <li><var>activity</var></li>
            <li><var>assessment</var></li>
            <li><var>location</var></li>
            <li><var>demographic</var></li>
            <li><var>financial</var></li>
            <li><var>health</var></li>
            <li><var>purchasing</var></li>
            <li><var>govid</var></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Types</h3>

        <ul>
            <li><var>system</var></li>
            <li><var>research</var></li>
            <li><var>profiling</var></li>
            <li><var>marketing</var></li>
            <li><var>context</var></li>
            <li><var>others</var></li>
            <li><var>public</var></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Values</h3>

        <ul>
            <li><var>true</var></li>
            <li><var>&quot;optOut&quot;</var></li>
            <li><var>&quot;optIn&quot;</var></li>
            <li><var>false</var></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Defaults</h3>

        <p>Logical defaults have been assumed to reduce the overall payload size. These defaults are meant to match expectations for a general "web app" that knows who a user is and what they're doing but that doesn't collect sensitive data such as used for purchasing or related to health or financial records.</p>

