            Privacy URL<br><small><dfn>1d5b3bbe-5715-4064-adb8-65209eeda3fe</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>1d5b3bbe-5715-4064-adb8-65209eeda3fe</var> is a string that defines the web-accessible location of a privacy statement for the application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="1d5b3bbe-5715-4064-adb8-65209eeda3fe"></pre>

        <p>The <a href="Attributes/Privacy#privacy">privacy</a> attribute is recommended over this one, but providing the link to a privacy policy is generally regarded as better than nothing at all.</p>

